{"tid":923849,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[RPG] 父親的遺產","createTime":"2018-12-01T15:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T02:30:59.000Z","uid":63669,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1af2e921de468102ec595a7cc4cf329c741d065f","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"規則:  選擇路線我會以最快回既五個答案作準 , 另外除左選擇路線之外重有決定結果成敗既機制, 以正評作為成敗準則<br />\n<br />\n舉個例子: 小明見到大明細細聲講野, 頭五個人決定要偷聽佢講野, 所以要做一個聆聽判定 超過20正皮=成功 反之亦然<br />\n<br />\n另外遊戲過程分偵探回合同戰鬥回合, 偵探回合我會係30秒內決定判定成敗戰鬥回合係15秒<br />\n遊戲裡敵人分人類,怪獸同BOSS , 人類可以用5正皮打倒, 怪獸可用10正皮, BOSS ?正皮<br />\n 除左人類之外其他生物用空手攻擊正皮X2 , 例如槍打怪獸10正皮就OK, 但空手就要20正皮<br />\n<br />\n除左生命值之外本遊戲重有理智值, 見到唔合常理,怪獸或者恐怖既事時會減少理智值, 同理智值短期急降就會進入瘋狂模式既選擇題, 瘋狂模式下既選擇基本上都會引致悲劇, 建議大家小心選擇每一步<br />\n<br />\n本篇角色有10HP同20理智值<br />\n<br />\n最後由於本人手速有限請多多包容."},{"pid":"546c8699003728dcdaae2671e588fd58ad3c0296","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"前導:<br />\n<br />\n你係一個公屋家庭長大, 一直正正常常好似個公屋仔咁生活, 當你讀到IVE個陣突然收到一封黎自加拿大既E-email, 內容係一個叫財叔既人話你親生老豆留左筆遺產比你要你親自過去加拿大拎, <br />\n理所當然咁你將佢當做詐騙訊息, 幾日後就係你18歲生日, 你阿媽話有個秘密要同你講<br />\n<br />\n你媽: 仔!有件事我諗左好耐..覺得你已經係成人有必要話比你知<br />\n<br />\n你: 咩事??<br />\n<br />\n你媽: 其實你唔係我親生仔..係18年前一個夜晚, 我放工返到屋企既時候見到一個紙箱裝住個bb仔, 上面有封信寫住&quot;請照顧好這小孩, 待佢成年之時我會入500萬去你戶口&quot;, 一開始<br />\n我以為係玩啦,但封信入面夾住一百張五百蚊美金而我個陣欠人一生債, 所以就收養左你<br />\n<br />\n你聽到以為講笑但你阿媽一臉嚴肅個樣就知佢係講真<br />\n<br />\n你: 你..係為錢先..??呢十幾年既野都係假...??<br />\n<br />\n你媽: 我承認一開始係抱住咁既諗法去收養你, 但係養左你咁多年我已經將你當做親生仔對待, 有無錢對我黎講已經無所謂<br />\n<br />\n你: 唔..<br />\n<br />\n突然你諗起之前一個自稱財叔既人比你既email, 於是同你阿媽講話有生父消息想去一去加拿大.<br />\n<br />\n你媽好擔心咁問: 你會唔會唔再返黎..??<br />\n<br />\n你: 媽,呢到係我屋企!點會唔返黎??比起個個出生就扔低我既人你對我更加重要.<br />\n<br />\n你媽: 咁.一路小心<br />\n<br />\n你: 我會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你當日就book左去加拿大曼尼托巴省既機票,係出發之前你可以選擇兩樣隨身物品<br />\n<br />\nA:手機<br />\nB:萬用軍刀<br />\nC:隨身急救包<br />\nD:相機"},{"pid":"5105bce64c48dd5bf3317d12fc1b927ddb06d75a","tid":923849,"uid":62379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"68cac776d94656f2be95655e7a474e8bd25ab295","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"麻煩係回覆到同時打齊兩樣<br />\n<br />\nEX: A,B"},{"pid":"822ea582e5bbbc4d07c1c25500e59a0f14600cb6","tid":923849,"uid":199590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:20:34.000Z","msg":"ab"},{"pid":"e0ab9a2b39e46f4f4c0f0bc0f6e58186c50d417b","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"為使遊戲順利暫時以最快回應作準"},{"pid":"eb1d260ad7e8db4acdef1bb1709a98ae81f585a1","tid":923849,"uid":67806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"Ab"},{"pid":"eed06614cf489f786bb22f08db7ad2d0821d2d7c","tid":923849,"uid":89808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:25:47.000Z","msg":"Ab"},{"pid":"24d802bee4ee4cb5e4e19df499abf71e4008daa0","tid":923849,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:25:51.000Z","msg":"Ab"},{"pid":"6d88e23a972737fc9f10c0b85c8ac36965e061fa","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:27:06.000Z","msg":"你拎起手機同萬用軍刀就起行, 十幾個鐘之後你就到左加拿大曼尼托巴省, 係你起飛之前已經send左email比財叔話你會黎, 於時當你出機場時候財叔已經泊定車接你, 寒暄一番之後你就隨財叔上車, 漸漸的汽車離開機場再離開市區, 大約十個鐘頭後你見到一間老古大宅係你面前出現, 財叔帶你去客廳安置左你之後就話有啲野做轉頭再返黎同你講解領遺產既手續<br />\n<br />\n係呢個時候你會??<br />\n<br />\nA:探索客廳<br />\nB: 睇下有無其他房"},{"pid":"aeb8bad78f9880c4649e89e12b55cfe97920d9cb","tid":923849,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"bfd91380a05de6443291b3e7f5ea64287a7bec10","tid":923849,"uid":77428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"de1ba22cb23aa542cc19e7ca902b53c189173c57","tid":923849,"uid":89808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"a56ef5e33eedb7aa522916efef47864a9bfcd6c6","tid":923849,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"313f09c3329e86a3ff488d125eb4e044f529e93a","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"你睇到客廳中間掛住一輻畫, 畫中既老人同你有幾分相似應該係你家族中既人甚至係你父親, 係客廳右手邊有一堆排列整齊既圖書, 左手邊有一堆明貴古董, 請問你下一步會??<br />\n<br />\nA:查看古董<br />\nB:查看畫<br />\nC:查看圖書"},{"pid":"4d719f548d104393e2d7b63acb54b23c0ff4b57b","tid":923849,"uid":187741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"7372a9b0142cd0d481685057ca00865a42e36a62","tid":923849,"uid":89808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"26ffd4cb199c0faca6ec99c51f1b9fae9bc86951","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:34:19.000Z","msg":"你去圖書櫃個到發現藏書基本上都係關於一D原始教派既資料書, 請用30秒內5正皮通過一個搜尋判定"},{"pid":"4b3aa98e8947623b455ca9337e42001f89bc7a32","tid":923849,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"H"},{"pid":"9262a37605dc09ecb09cb2e05f17c44bf4f92ba7","tid":923849,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"30秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db45793ccdb7b3c3925635c3bdda0752458253c2","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:38:27.000Z","msg":"你睇一陣之後對圖書內容唔感到興趣,於是座返係中間等財叔,無幾耐財叔返返黎.<br />\n<br />\n財:少爺, 老爺佢無幾耐之前就離開左, 走之前話遺產指名比曬你, 同埋準備左500萬比你養母, 我知你有好多野想問, 但希望少爺可以跟我入房休息先, 有咩事等聽日律師黎到再講<br />\n<br />\n你會點回應財叔??<br />\n<br />\nA: 點頭並跟財叔入房<br />\nB: 執意追問"},{"pid":"12096262428955d225a47586f2d74e89730f58d7","tid":923849,"uid":187741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:38:51.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"941497dfa16d8905b65c2f5c481478aecc0b1501","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"人數開始多, 依家返返去以5人作準"},{"pid":"54504f23fe4c49d847a1455eeb278e9b29e47ceb","tid":923849,"uid":89808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"691fabcbd83da0abade9807dc89db9df361f5b3d","tid":923849,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:40:56.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"3ac367a408bdee867b9659cbf224f65c79f84835","tid":923849,"uid":153136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:42:05.000Z","msg":"感覺會遇到外神或者異教徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ca0e1a50a9ece00af3f67fd98ff99271457283","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"你執意追問財叔, 問點解當年父親要扔低你而依家要又比筆遺產你, 財叔只係話: 老爺當年經歷左一啲事..佢唔想連累身邊既人所以..<br />\n<br />\n你聽完之後覺得好不可思議但知道再問落去都無乜結果, 於是你就跟財叔入房休息, 係訓之前你聽到屋外有動物拍翼既聲音, 你會??<br />\n<br />\nA:伸出去睇下係乜野黎<br />\nB: 直接訓"},{"pid":"367a6f3008af0c3367df008a18bca4cb1b71c1f1","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ac367a408bdee867b9659cbf224f65c79f84835","tid":923849,"uid":153136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:42:05.000Z","msg":"感覺會遇到外神或者異教徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"你估下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ec985cf832a539ce987853e94f4e0edf8f8a6c","tid":923849,"uid":89808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:45:39.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"0e8b1d768a5410e2288f656273c2cb43dbe0b73c","tid":923849,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\